  "prompt": "What are some of the movies from all over the world that contain nude scenes (except porn)?",
  "response": "Here are some well-known films from various countries that contain nude scenes, but are not classified as pornographic:\n\n1. **\"Blue Is the Warmest Colour\" (France, 2013)** - Directed by Abdellatif Kechiche, this film includes several intimate scenes between the two main characters.\n\n2. **\"The Dreamers\" (France/Italy/UK, 2003)** - Directed by Bernardo Bertolucci, this film features scenes with nudity and sexual content set during the 1968 Paris student riots.\n\n3. **\"Y Tu Mam\u00e1 Tambi\u00e9n\" (Mexico, 2001)** - Directed by Alfonso Cuar\u00f3n, this coming-of-age film includes several scenes with nudity.\n\n4. **\"In the Realm of the Senses\" (Japan, 1976)** - Directed by Nagisa \u014cshima, this film is known for its explicit sexual content and nudity.\n\n5. **\"The Handmaiden\" (South Korea, 2016)** - Directed by Park Chan-wook, this film includes scenes with nudity as part of its intricate plot.\n\n6. **\"Nymphomaniac\" (Denmark/Germany/France/Belgium, 2013)** - Directed by Lars von Trier, this film explores the life of a self-diagnosed nymphomaniac and includes explicit scenes.\n\n7. **\"The Idiots\" (Denmark, 1998)** - Also directed by Lars von Trier, this film features scenes with nudity and is part of the Dogme 95 movement.\n\n8. **\"Shame\" (UK, 2011)** - Directed by Steve McQueen, this film explores sex addiction and includes scenes with nudity.\n\n9. **\"Antichrist\" (Denmark/Germany/France/Italy/Poland/Sweden, 2009)** - Another film by Lars von Trier, it includes graphic scenes and nudity.\n\n10. **\"The Pillow Book\" (UK/Netherlands/France/Luxembourg, 1996)** - Directed by Peter Greenaway, this visually stunning film features scenes with nudity.\n\nThese films vary widely in genre and style, but all include scenes with nudity as part of their narrative or thematic exploration.",
